│ The legacy cost model might overestimate costs for certain scalable operations compared to the VPlan model. Additionally, the loop has a dead branch (`br i1 false`) and a constant phi that simplifies to 0.  │
│ The VPlan may have optimized this more aggressively, but `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` might not detect this because the instructions are still present (just with constant propagation).            │
